{"id": "1440500173187846218", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "320791943712079872", "author_name": "onoyasumi", "content": "I really appreciate your transparency, and I completely understand how difficult it is for the devs to balance gameplay experience and player satisfaction/retention. Especially during a critical window like the anniversary.\n\nAs a newer player, I happened to be on Arc 1 Chapter 9 right before the nerf, and it was a bit shocking how easy it was to defeat the final bosses. The story sadly lost some of its impact for me because it wasn't challenging, so I agree that the nerf was too drastic. But I'm still very happy to support the game, and I have faith that you and the dev team will find a good balance eventually. Wishing you well!", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T00:33:24.487000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1440393579121082378", "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "⬆️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "reply_to": "1440426330016583760"}
{"id": "1440501783700177059", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "284786355068731392", "author_name": "dragoon2323", "content": "You can have both modes, just call one easy mode and the other normal. As someone who started becuase this gacha was advertised as being semi difficult it’s disappointing how braindead the new difficulty is", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T00:39:48.463000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1440393579121082378", "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤝", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}], "reply_to": "1440426330016583760"}
{"id": "1440502396986851380", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "320791943712079872", "author_name": "onoyasumi", "content": "Yeah, the best long-term solution might be an easy mode to help onboard new players and improve accessibility. That or a higher gnosis limit could help. But it'll probably have to wait until after anniversary", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T00:42:14.682000+00:00", "thread_id": "1440393579121082378", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-19T00:44:52.333000+00:00"}
{"id": "1440518792722776145", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "content": "Alright. I'll give my own arguments a counter argument. Pertaining specifically to the situation of my friends who have problems with the balancing now.\n\nA lot of them have been just doing dailies, trapbase and events for a while. Waiting for the patch and still expecting the same/similar difficulty.\n\nTheir units are a lot more built up then new players have at those points of the game...\n\nSo the normal mode balancing might be fine... As much as I hate to admit it...", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T01:47:23.730000+00:00", "thread_id": "1440393579121082378"}
