{"id": "1440522516245385367", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "content": "Plus new players using guides will have hypercarries that nuke the hardest bosses in a turn... At this rate bringing back cacoon isn't that bad of an idea either. <:takenotes:1357186646294138890> \n\nNew players past ch9 can tell me if I'm wrong about this.", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T02:02:11.487000+00:00", "thread_id": "1440393579121082378", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-19T02:02:18.212000+00:00"}
{"id": "1440526160436924520", "channel_id": "1440393579121082378", "author_id": "212587018436345856", "author_name": "nactra", "content": "Can't comment on the business side because i don't know what you know - but must say that i am playing this game solely because it is challenging while giving a lot of tools and agency to the player. While you pinned a statement about comitting to offering challenge in new/top tier content - i am worried about the many signs of slop (auto battle, brainrot onboarding through rewards, absurd nerf) i am seeing. I left Wuwa in 1.3-1.4 when it became slop instead of genshin but its dark souls, and i would be sad about having to leave Morimens soon because it became slop instead of slay the spire but live service. Give me ridiculous complexity and 40 minutes turns Astrea style, clearing bosses in 1 hour and 28 turns with high stakes back and forth is why im playing. Based on my attempt at playing story today i just want to stop playing, because i cant call it playing, i click on buttons then i win. Please stay elitist, and accept that the bottom 20% weaklings dont belong here, minimum. Nerfing to be a little more welcoming is understandable, attempting to capture a \"wider audience\" is a mistake.\n\nNew Pdive being calibrated around speed clearing/efficiency only is also disappointing on the other hand of the spectum- i want to explore slow, deliberate playstyles, and perform crazy combos, not just see red numbers go up through nukes\n\nWe have a lot of awakeners and creatice team combinations that are possible, but if the only way to improve performance is nukes, then why ?", "timestamp": "2025-11-19T02:16:40.330000+00:00", "thread_id": "1440393579121082378", "reactions": [{"emoji": "proud", "emoji_id": "1400771808356991057", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "dizzy", "emoji_id": "1356053061508010156", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}]}
